citeinfo.othercit: UO InfoGraphics Lab converted original source images (GeoTIFFs) to ArcSDE raster dataset.

descript.abstract: This file displays the location and shape of the buildings at the University of Oregon campus- Eugene, Oregon. The data in this feature class was geocoded from the 2004 Aerial Photograph. This dataset is stored is an AcrSDE feature class in SQL.
descript.purpose: Dataset was produced for the purpose of planning, mapping and facilities maintenance of the University of Oregon
descript.supplinf: This dataset is stored in the InfoGraphics Campus Geodatabase - housed in 163 Condon.
